      "@id": "https://data.datatourisme.fr/8cf97970-c51c-3fc3-a2ee-2b085cf7ed21",
      "dc:description": {
        "de": [
          "Der Wochenmarkt mit lokalen Produkten und handwerklichen Kreationen findet jeden Freitag von 16:30 bis 19:00 Uhr auf dem Place de l'Eglise statt."
        ],
        "en": [
          "Save the date!\nThe new weekly market of local produce and handmade creations kicks off on Friday 13 October!\nIt will take place every Friday, from 4pm, in rue des Tennis (near the Carrefour express and tennis courts).\nFor this first event, the professionals on hand will be offering :\n- bread and buns\n- oysters\n- vegetables\n- meats,\n- food-truck burgers/sweet pancakes\n- and decorations, accessories and jewellery.\nOther products will be added to the market over time: cheese, honey, spirulina, cider and apple juice, etc.\n \nIf you would like to join the market, please contact us on 02 97 24 60 87 - accueil@locoal-mendon.fr \nWe look forward to seeing you there!"
        ],
        "it": [
          "Il mercato settimanale di prodotti locali e creazioni artigianali si tiene ogni venerdì dalle 16.30 alle 19.00 in Place de l'Église."
        ],
        "fr": [
          "Le marché hebdomadaire de produits locaux et de créations artisanales se tient tous les vendredis de 16h30 à 19h,  sur la place de l'Église."
        ],
        "es": [
          "El mercado semanal de productos locales y creaciones artesanales se celebra todos los viernes de 16.30 a 19.00 horas en la plaza de l'Église."
        ],
        "nl": [
          "De wekelijkse markt met lokale producten en handgemaakte creaties wordt elke vrijdag van 16.30 tot 19.00 uur gehouden op de Place de l'Église."
        ]
      },
